messages.content: No, not stopping in New Zealand. I would want to, but it's pretty expensive flying anywhere out of Marshall Islands. So I'll just fly straight to US. But thanks for offering, and for remembering that I wanted to do that.

Andy!
Bro, I just thought to ask you if you're stopping in on New Zealand anytime as you end your time in the S Pacific. I can connect you with people there, if you like.
Peace in the Lord,
-Brian
